8. Implement import/export functionality for bulk operations
9. Add duplicate prevention mechanism
10. Create client communication integration (direct call, email)

Client data model should include:
```typescript
interface Client {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  email: string;
  phone: string;
  address: {
    street: string;
    city: string;
    state: string;
    postalCode: string;
    country: string;
  };
  vatNumber?: string;
  fiscalCode?: string;
  isCompany: boolean;
  notes?: string;
  createdAt: Date;
  updatedAt: Date;
}
```

